               <msContents>
                  <summary>Book of Hours of Abba Giyorgis, መጽሐፈ፡ ሰዓታት፡  ዘአባ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡, produced in the government scriptorium</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="82r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT3575Mashaf"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሰዳዴሆሙ፡ ለአጋንንት፡ እምየማንነ፡ ወእምፀጋምነ፡ ወእዛቲ፡ መካንነ፡ ይርኅቁ፡ እምኔነ፡ ለእለ፡ ይፀብዕዋ፡ ለነፍስነ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
